---
/**
 * Hero 섹션
 * @TASK P2-S1-T1
 * @SPEC docs/planning/06-screens.md#1.2-히어로-섹션
 *
 * 기능:
 * - hero-gradient 배경 + tech-pattern
 * - blur 효과 (bg-blue-500/10 blur-[120px])
 * - 메인 캐치프레이즈: "AI로 더 빠르게, 관세사로 더 정확하게"
 * - 서브 카피: 해외 수출 인증·허가 안내
 * - CTA: [무료 견적 받기], [서비스 보기]
 */
---

<section
  id="hero"
  class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center hero-gradient overflow-hidden"
>
  <!-- Background Pattern -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 tech-pattern opacity-30"></div>

  <!-- Blur Effects -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/4 -right-20 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 -left-20 w-96 h-96 bg-indigo-500/10 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <!-- Badge -->
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-white/10 rounded-full mb-8 backdrop-blur-sm">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-400 text-sm">verified</span>
      <span class="text-sm font-medium text-white/90">전문 관세사 운영 · 전문가배상책임보험 가입</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Headline -->
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
      AI로 더 빠르게,<br />
      <span class="text-blue-400">관세사로 더 정확하게</span>
    </h1>

    <!-- Sub Copy -->
    <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/80 mb-4 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      해외 수출 인증·허가, 이제 합리적인 비용으로 시작하세요
    </p>
    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-white/60 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      FDA, EU, 일본 인증부터 통관까지 원스톱 지원
    </p>

    <!-- CTA Buttons -->
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a
        href="#cta"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 sm:px-10 py-4 sm:py-5 bg-white text-navy rounded-xl font-bold text-base sm:text-lg hover:shadow-2xl hover:scale-105 transition-all"
      >
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl">mail</span>
        무료 견적 받기
      </a>
      <a
        href="#services"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 sm:px-10 py-4 sm:py-5 bg-transparent border border-white/30 text-white rounded-xl font-bold text-base sm:text-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-all"
      >
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl">arrow_downward</span>
        서비스 보기
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 sm:gap-8 mt-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">160만원</div>
        <div class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-white/60 mt-1">FDA 인증</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">30일</div>
        <div class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-white/60 mt-1">평균 처리 기간</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">11년</div>
        <div class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-white/60 mt-1">관세사 경력</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Scroll Indicator -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce">
    <a href="#value-proposition" class="text-white/50 hover:text-white/80 transition-colors">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">keyboard_arrow_down</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
